Package gw.api.databuilder

Class TaxIdGenerator

java.lang.Object
gw.api.databuilder.TaxIdGenerator
All Implemented Interfaces:
ValueGenerator<String>
public class TaxIdGenerator extends Object implements ValueGenerator<String>
Generates random Tax ID values that are localized to the specified country. This is SSN specific, it uses the Validator.SSN. It is used by Person and Person subtypes in countries where the tax identifier does not have the same format for individuals and companies.
Author:
bspies
